OL,3,  Kefir for Health and Security   Q "###
OL,4,C The Ministry of Food Standards has    
OL,5,C announced a programme requiring the   
OL,6,C citizens of Residential Sector 7 to   
OL,7,C consume 500ml of individually coded   
OL,8, CKefir ration every week.              
OL,10,  HOW IT WORKS:FEach citizen is given a 
OL,11,F unique microbial blend of Kefir. As   
OL,12,F well as promoting gut health a toilet 
OL,13,F sensor analyses the microbial biome.  
OL,15,  HEALTHY GUTS:FSABRE toilet sensors    
OL,16,F instantly test for any abnormalities  
OL,17,F and report them to The Orakle AI.     
OL,19,  CITIZEN TRACKING:FEach Kefir has a    
OL,20,F unique microbial "barcode" blend.     
OL,21,F SABRE can track without cameras.      
